			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">BASIC CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Move character:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad or Left Analog Stick</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Talk, search for items, take the helm of the dragon ship or Gwyn's boat, exit the dragon ship:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Run, cancel commands during combat:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Normal menu, board the dragon ship:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Return to previous screen:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Run for a few seconds:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L3 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Menu / Skip sequence:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Select Button</font>
